Hi!

I discovered this great app!

PsyTrack Clinician Tools in iTunes

Thanks to everyone who supported and encouraged me as a made this app. A special thanks to Dr. Shalene Kirkley Ph.D. for her encouragement and enthusiasm for pursuing the idea back in the first year of my doctorate program. I have had a lot of fun making it and I am glad to finally be able to share it with all of you. Thank you Edwin Nez for all your bug testing and patience with me while I made the app. Thanks also to Dr. Benson-Florez Ph.D. for his multicultural suggestions. Thank YOU for trying my app and hopefully writing a cheritable review for me. I hope that you find it useful and enjoyable to use. Thank you Tarek Sakr at Sensible Table view for a great product and support, and thanks to Dr. Touch at Cocoanetics for his help with the DTAboutViewController. Thank you Krishna Kotecha for the starting point for the lock screen. Thanks to Julius Oklamcak for the starting point for the pdf viewer. Thanks to Chick Arnold for giving me idea about tracking the media appearances. Thank you to Apple, Inc. and all their laborers around the world for a making all of this amazing technology possible. And of course, thanks friends and family for their constant support throughout my life.
